general_advice: Infertility is when a couple cannot get pregnant (conceive) despite having regular unprotected sex.

Around 1 in 7 couples may have difficulty conceiving. If you have been trying naturally for a baby for less than 1 year and you are less than 35 years old you may continue for a total of one year.|Please continue to have a healthy lifestyle and avoid smoking and alcohol consumption.
